# React E-Commerce Website

A modern, responsive e-commerce web application created with the assistance of **Google AI Studio** and customized, deployed, and maintained by me. The project demonstrates modern frontend development practices, REST API integration, responsive UI design, cloud deployment, and version control.

## 🚀 Features

* Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop
* Product listing and product details
* Search functionality
* Shopping cart management
* REST API integration
* Component-based React architecture
* Clean and modern UI
* Cross-browser compatibility

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* React.js
* JavaScript (ES6+)
* HTML5
* CSS3
* React Router
* REST APIs
* Git & GitHub
* Google Cloud Run

## 👨‍💻 My Contributions

* Customized and refined the generated application.
* Integrated and configured REST APIs.
* Improved the UI/UX and responsiveness.
* Tested functionality and fixed issues.
* Managed source code with Git and GitHub.
* Deployed the application on Google Cloud Run.

> **Note:** The initial project structure was generated with assistance from Google AI Studio. The application was customized, configured, tested, and deployed by me as part of my frontend development portfolio.
